      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Day 2 of the Carnival and there might be some sore heads on the back-up after Cup Day and this race won't help alleviate any headaches. Looks the best opportunity yet for CODENAME (2) to break the duck. Been racing consistently on the Vic provincial circuit in races that have had a bit more depth than this. Similar story with RENEGE (5), who has had 20 goes but just struggles to break through. Has placed eight times though, including last start when she found only one better and a repeat of that would see her go close here. DEFY GRAVITY (3) is one of a couple of Croweaters crossing the border and while he hasn't placed in three starts, he hasn't been beaten all that far at his past couple and will find this class of race to his liking. NAUGHTY JAMIE (6) is the debutant in the field who hasn't set the world on fire at the trials but strikes a suitable debut option. Watch market. BRAZEN MARTINI (1) trialled ok recently, but race form is poor.",
